_header: When Zephyrus eke with his fresh tarage
Subjects: love, praise of; love, vicissitudes of; love, game of; love, constancy in
_description: Humfrey Newton, A love adventure praising love — ten quatrains

BodLatMisC66.First Lines:
When ȝepheres eeke withe his fresshe taragehas concluded
                    wentur in a breef space…
BodLatMisC66.Last Lines:
…Bot when we han merely met in pleke or in placewyth meloduous
                    tunys I shall meyne with my moth
